column5: Hello All, I'm heading up to Dickie lake in a couple of weeks, and can't seem to find to much info on it. Any idea what I should expect, types of fish,. numbers, size, etc? Any tips, or spots greatly appreciated. Thanks!
Large and small mouth bass, pike, perch according to Fish Online
Thanks- Hopefully there is some size!
fished lake of bays september 2nd last year, bass were hard on the shiner bite. suspending out in 50fow
Thanks- might be a tricky tactic in a canoe with no electronics, but I'll give it a go.
